-- All NZX markets halted due to messaging issues
-- By Naomi Tajitsu
-- Thu Jun 26, 2014 06:39PM EDT
-- None



WELLINGTON, June 27 (Reuters) - New Zealand's stock exchange <NZX.NZ> on Friday said that all of its markets including the benchmark NZX-50 <.NZ50> had been halted due to issues regarding its FIX messaging system.

